#

Mushroom and Spinach Crepes

30 min
$12.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh Protein

Cuisine:

French

Course:

Main

Tags:

BrunchLight MealSavoryComfort Food

Description

Delicate crepes filled with a savory mix of sautéed mushrooms and spinach, topped with a creamy sauce for a perfect brunch or light dinner.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • eggs: 2
  • milk: 1 1/4 cups
  • water: 1/4 cup
  • butter: 3 tablespoons
  • fresh spinach: 2 cups
  • mushrooms: 2 cups
  • cream cheese: 4 ounces
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • nutmeg: a pinch
